metadata.name: GAZE
metadata.description:
Dearest reader, 

I'm sure you are wondering why 'LADY WHITE', here it is.
We all know you being different in our world is not exactly welcome at first. With an appearance unlike the norm, one that made the heroine repulsive to the ton, it was a tedious task finding where she belonged.
Little did we know, her peculiarity would make her desirable to all in the near future. 
In the face of antipathy, the beauty of her skin never faded, neither did her view on life change. She walked with a grace unlike any others. She had the ton abuzz after every of her promenade. Her gaze has effects words can't express.
All along, her news had travelled, beyond the country's edge. Suitors came seeking to meet this odd beauty, one white as snow. The game had begun, the battle for the diamond of the season. This would turn out to be an exciting season for her, the beguiling Lady White.
